title: Move in today! 2x2 w/ lake view & granite countertops available!
posting_body: ['At Tennis Towers Apartments, you’ll find superior comfort, stylish design, and touches of elegance everywhere you look.', 'From spacious, well-appointed interiors and lush landscaping, to first-rate features and an incredible location, our apartments for rent West Palm Beach, FL truly have it all.', 'Our extensive list of amenities includes a tropical swimming pool & spa, a 24-hour fitness center, and a charming barbecue picnic area.', 'Of course, Tennis Towers wouldn’t be complete without three lighted tennis courts.', 'Minutes from the beach and surrounded by a vast array of convenient shops, delicious restaurants, and endless entertainment opportunities, everything you need is always right at your fingertips when you choose our stunning apartments.', "West Palm Beach's Tennis Towers welcomes to the living experience of a lifetime.", 'Call/text for more information!', 'show contact info', 'You can also visit our website to apply online: <URL>']
